doctype html
html(lang='en')

    head

        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='')
        meta(name='author', content='')

        title Eric's Blog

        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/logo.png')

        // Font Awesome icons (free version)
        script(src='https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.15.3/js/all.js', crossorigin='anonymous')

        // Google fonts
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lora:400,700,400italic,700italic', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300italic,400italic,600italic,700italic,800italic,400,300,600,700,800', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')

        // Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)
        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')

    body

        // Navigation
        nav#mainNav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-light.fixed-top
            .container
                img(src="assets/logo.png" width="50" height="50")
                a.navbar-brand(href='index.html') Eric Wu 
                button.navbar-toggler.navbar-toggler-right(type='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-target='#navbarResponsive', aria-controls='navbarResponsive', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                    | Menu
                    i.fas.fa-bars
                #navbarResponsive.collapse.navbar-collapse
                    ul.navbar-nav.ml-auto
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='index.html') Home
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='about.html') About
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='project.html') Project
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='contact.html') Contact
        // Page Header
        header.masthead(style="background-image: url('assets/img/project-bg.jpg')")
            .overlay
            .container
                .row
                    .col-lg-8.col-md-10.mx-auto
                        .page-heading
                            h1 My work
                            span.subheading Here's what I have done.
        // Main Content
        section
            #flexbox.container
                .card
                    .card-img-top 
                        img(src="assets/img/gis-record-searching-system-in-c-plus-plus/banner.jpg") 
                    .card-body
                        small.card-text.text-muted Posted on April 12, 2021
                        h5.card-title GIS record searching system in C++
                        p.card-text Implment a GIS record searching system with Hashtable + PR quadtree + bufferpool
                    a(href="/post/2021-04-12-gis-record-searching-system-in-c-plus-plus.html" role="button" aria-pressed="true").rounded-lg.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm.active View Post
                .card
                    .card-img-top 
                        img(src="assets/img/sudoku-solver-in-c-plus-plus/banner.jpg") 
                    .card-body
                        small.card-text.text-muted Posted on April 11, 2021
                        h5.card-title Sodoku Solver in C++
                        p.card-text Implement a Sudoku solver with alogrithm X + dancing links (brute force)
                    a(href="/post/2021-04-11-sudoku-solver-in-c-plus-plus.html" role="button" aria-pressed="true").rounded-lg.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm.active View Post
                .card
                    .card-img-top 
                        img(src="assets/img/exploiting-bluetooth-ctkd-vulnerability/banner.jpg") 
                    .card-body
                        small.card-text.text-muted Posted on April 03, 2021
                        h5.card-title Exploiting Bluetooth CTKD vulnerability
                        p.card-text The discovered Bluetooth vulnerability (CVE-2020-15802) makes it possible for attacker to steal Bluetooth session
                    a(href="/post/2021-04-03-exploiting-bluetooth-ctkd-vulnerability.html" role="button" aria-pressed="true").rounded-lg.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm.active View Post
                .card
                    .card-img-top 
                        img(src="assets/img/covert-channel-application/banner.jpg") 
                    .card-body
                        small.card-text.text-muted Posted on December 7, 2020
                        h5.card-title Covert Channel Application
                        p.card-text Implement a complete covert application that allow a user to access a port on a firewall, communicate with a "disguised" backdoor
                    a(href="/post/2020-12-07-covert-channel-application.html" role="button" aria-pressed="true").rounded-lg.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm.active View Post
                .card
                    .card-img-top 
                        img(src="assets/img/dns-spoofing-application/banner.jpg") 
                    .card-body
                        small.card-text.text-muted Posted on November 10, 2020
                        h5.card-title DNS Spoofing Application
                        p.card-text Design & implement a basic DNS spoofing application
                    a(href="/post/2020-11-10-dns-spoofing-application.html" role="button" aria-pressed="true").rounded-lg.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm.active View Post
                .card
                    .card-img-top 
                        img(src="assets/img/packet-sniffing-backdoor/banner.jpg") 
                    .card-body
                        small.card-text.text-muted Posted on October 30, 2020
                        h5.card-title Packet Sniffing Backdoor
                        p.card-text Establish a communication channel between a victim's machine and a attacker's machine
                    a(href="/post/2020-10-30-packet-sniffing-backdoor.html" role="button" aria-pressed="true").rounded-lg.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm.active View Post
                .card
                    .card-img-top 
                        img(src="assets/img/image-steganography/banner.jpg") 
                    .card-body
                        small.card-text.text-muted Posted on October 11, 2020
                        h5.card-title Image Steganography
                        p.card-text Implement an application that allows users to encrypt a secret image, and embed it into a cover image
                    a(href="/post/2020-10-11-image-steganography.html" role="button" aria-pressed="true").rounded-lg.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm.active View Post
                .card
                    .card-img-top 
                        img(src="assets/img/port-forwarder/banner.jpg") 
                    .card-body
                        small.card-text.text-muted Posted on April 12, 2020
                        h5.card-title Port Forwarder
                        p.card-text Design and develop a network application that uses advanced TCP/IP programming techniques, and implement a "Port Forwarder" using  C languange
                    a(href="/post/2020-04-12-port-forwarder.html" role="button" aria-pressed="true").rounded-lg.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm.active View Post
                .card
                    .card-img-top 
                        img(src="assets/img/compare-epoll-with-select-server/banner.jpg") 
                    .card-body
                        small.card-text.text-muted Posted on January 15, 2020
                        h5.card-title Compare Epoll with Select server
                        p.card-text compare the scalability and performance of the select and epoll-based client server implementations
                    a(href="/post/2020-01-15-compare-epoll-with-select-server.html" role="button" aria-pressed="true").rounded-lg.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm.active View Post
        hr
        // Footer
        footer
            .container
                .row
                    .col-lg-8.col-md-10.mx-auto
                        ul.list-inline.text-center
                            li.list-inline-item
                                a(href='https://linkedin.com/in/ericwu1997')
                                    span.fa-stack.fa-lg
                                        i.fas.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
                                        i.fab.fa-linkedin.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
                            li.list-inline-item
                                a(href='https://github.com/ericwu1997')
                                    span.fa-stack.fa-lg
                                        i.fas.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
                                        i.fab.fa-github.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
                        p.copyright.text-muted Copyright &copy; Your Website 2021

